Package: datetimeoffset
Type: Package
Title: Datetimes with optional UTC offsets and/or heterogeneous time zones
Version: 0.1.0-4
Authors@R: c(
        person("Trevor L", "Davis", role=c("aut", "cre"), email="trevor.l.davis@gmail.com",
               comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6341-4639")))
Description: Datetimes with optional UTC offsets and/or (possibly heterogeneous) time zones.
    Supports import/export for a number of datetime string standards often including lossless re-export of     
    any original reduced precision including ISO 8601 and pdfmark datetime strings.
    Can support up to nanosecond precision.
URL: https://trevorldavis.com/R/datetimeoffset/dev/, https://github.com/trevorld/r-datetimeoffset
BugReports: https://github.com/trevorld/r-datetimeoffset
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
